title: The Very Hungry Caterpillar 30 in. Kids 4-Piece Garden Tool Set Hoe, Shovel, Leaf Rake, Garden Rake
description: The Very Hungry Caterpillar Garden Tool Set: A shovel, a hoe, and 2 types of rakes compile the perfect first gardening set for kids. The large tools can help prepare soil, dig up treasures (and worms)and create the perfect space for new growth. Colorful and constructed with care, this set makes gardening and exploring even more enjoyable for the newest of gardeners.
